      "amount": "2 teaspoons"
    },
    {
      "name": "Turmeric Powder",
      "amount": "1/4 teaspoon"
    }
  ],
  "instructions": [
    "Heat olive oil in a wok or large frying pan over medium heat.",
    "Add onion and garlic, sauté for about 3 minutes until softened.",
    "Stir in tomato paste, water chestnuts, lemon juice, red pepper flakes, cumin seeds, and turmeric powder. Cook for another minute.",
    "Add shrimp to the sauce, cook for 2-3 minutes or until fully cooked.",
    "Blend Greek yogurt with a splash of water and add it to the pan. Stir continuously until the mixture thickens slightly, about 1-2 minutes.",
    "Garnish with saffron threads if using.",
    "Serve hot over steamed basmati rice."
  ],
